04806D62.Line8.103673: May the Light guide your way.

673744FD.Line3.103673: I must return to Zarbinzet. I shall tell the other Zakarum of Carthas and the paladins who gave their lives to contain Mephisto's corruption.

8EB39B3B.Line1.103673: Yes, (deep breath) I believe so. The paladins are finally at peace. I could not have done this alone. The Light shines bright within you.

DEE9C708.VoiceDir1.103673: Tired, but still full of spirit.
